service.tut.pori.contentanalysis

Class PhotoParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.AbstractTaskDetails.TaskParameters
      • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.PhotoParameters

  • public final class PhotoParameters
extends AbstractTaskDetails.TaskParameters
    Analysis parameters for an analysis task.

    Optional Elements

    • analysisTypeList. If not given, the defaults PhotoParameters.AnalysisType.KEYWORD_EXTRACTION and PhotoParameters.AnalysisType.VISUAL should be used.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<taskParameters>
  <analysisTypeList>
    <analysisType>FACE_DETECTION</analysisType>
    <analysisType>KEYWORD_EXTRACTION</analysisType>
    <analysisType>VISUAL</analysisType>
  </analysisTypeList>
</taskParameters>
